INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (71, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '我的周末治愈食记｜在家复刻一碗日式豚骨拉面', '花 3 小时熬一锅汤，慢下来感受做饭的治愈感，比外卖香 100 倍！', 'upload/news_picture1.jpg', '<p>周末不想出门，决定挑战一下日式豚骨拉面，从熬汤到煮面，全程自己动手，成就感拉满！</p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">耗时</strong>：3 小时（主要是熬汤时间长）</p><p> <strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">步骤分享</strong>：</p><ol><li>猪筒骨提前焯水，加姜葱小火熬煮 2.5 小时，熬出奶白色的浓汤。</li><li>提前腌好的叉烧肉切片，溏心蛋煮到 6 分熟，剥壳备用。</li><li>煮好的拉面捞出，倒入浓汤，码上叉烧、溏心蛋、海苔、葱花，最后淋一勺辣椒油。喝一口热汤，吃一口筋道的面条，所有疲惫都被治愈了～虽然麻烦，但自己做的料超足，健康又好吃，推荐大家周末试试！</li></ol><p><br></p>', 15);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (72, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '为什么中国人过年一定要吃饺子？ 藏在饺子里的年俗文化', '小小的饺子里，藏着中国人最朴素的团圆与祝福。', 'upload/news_picture2.jpg', '<p>过年吃饺子，是刻在中国人 DNA 里的仪式感，这背后藏着千年的文化寓意：</p><ol><li><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">形状像元宝</strong>：饺子的外形酷似古代元宝，过年吃饺子寓意「招财进宝」，新的一年财源滚滚。</li><li><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">谐音「交子」</strong>：「饺子」谐音「交子」，代表新旧交替，在除夕夜零点吃饺子，寓意「更岁交子」，辞旧迎新。</li><li><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">团圆的象征</strong>：一家人围在一起包饺子，擀皮、调馅、捏褶，每一个步骤都是家人间的互动，代表着团圆和睦。不同地区还有不同习俗：北方爱吃猪肉白菜馅，南方会加虾仁、韭菜，有些地方还会在饺子里包硬币，吃到的人新一年会有好运～今年过年，你家包的是什么馅？</li></ol><p><br></p>', 15);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (73, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '别再乱买了！一篇看懂「生抽 / 老抽 / 蚝油」的区别', '厨房新手最容易搞混的三种调料，用法、区别一次讲清楚！', 'upload/news_picture3.jpg', '<p>很多人做饭时分不清生抽、老抽、蚝油，其实它们的作用完全不同：</p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">生抽</strong>：提鲜 + 上色浅，适合凉拌、炒菜、蘸料，味道偏咸鲜，日常用得最多。</p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">老抽</strong>：上色 + 提味，颜色深、味道偏甜，适合红烧、卤味，放一点点就能让菜品色泽红亮。</p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">蚝油</strong>：提鲜 + 增稠，由牡蛎熬制而成，适合炒青菜、焖肉、勾芡，能让汤汁更浓郁，但要注意最后放，避免煮久发苦。</p><p>小技巧：炒菜时先放生抽提味，出锅前放蚝油增鲜；做红烧菜先放老抽上色，再用生抽调味。收藏起来，下次做饭再也不会用错啦！</p>', 15);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (74, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '厨房小白必看！3 个让家常菜瞬间变好吃的技巧', '不用复杂调料，3 个基础技巧让你的家常菜香味翻倍、口感升级！', 'upload/news_picture4.jpg', '<p><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">腌肉去腥提嫩</strong>：腌肉时加少许料酒 + 白胡椒粉 + 淀粉，抓匀后静置 10 分钟，炒出来的肉又嫩又入味，完全不柴。</p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">炒青菜保绿脆</strong>：大火快炒，出锅前淋一小勺香油 + 少许盐，既能锁住绿色，又能让口感更脆爽，避免发黄发软。</p><p><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">熬汤增鲜秘诀</strong>：熬骨汤时加一小块冰糖 + 几片干香菇，不用放味精，汤头自然鲜甜，还能中和油腻感。</p><p>亲测有效！新手也能一次成功，快试试吧～</p><p><br></p>', 15);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (75, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '零失败！让米饭粒粒分明的 3 个蒸饭小技巧', '告别黏糊糊的米饭，厨房小白也能蒸出餐厅级口感！', 'upload/news_picture5.jpg', '<p>每次蒸米饭都要么太硬要么太黏？试试这 3 个小技巧，保证粒粒分明、香软可口：</p><ol><li><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">提前浸泡</strong>：大米提前用清水浸泡 30 分钟，让米粒充分吸水，蒸出来更饱满。</li><li><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">精准控水</strong>：米和水的比例控制在 1:1.2（大概是手指没过大米第一节指节），避免水多软烂。</li><li><strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">焖饭关键</strong>：电饭煲跳闸后不要马上开盖，继续焖 10 分钟，让米饭充分吸收余温，口感更筋道。</li></ol><p>进阶技巧：加几滴香油或一小片柠檬，米饭会更清香，还能防粘！</p><p><br></p>', 15);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (76, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '一碗面里的江湖｜中国不同地域的吃面哲学', '从北到南，中国人的面条里藏着地域性格与生活烟火。\n', 'upload/news_picture6.jpg', '<p>中国是「面条大国」，不同地区的面条，藏着不一样的生活态度：</p><p> <strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">北方</strong>：以「筋道」为魂，比如兰州拉面的一清二白三红四绿，讲究面的弹性与汤的醇厚，是北方人豪爽的体现。</p><p> <strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">西南</strong>：以「麻辣」为骨，重庆小面、宜宾燃面，重调料重香气，是西南人热烈直爽的味觉表达。</p><p> <strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">华中</strong>：以「干香」为韵，武汉热干面的芝麻酱拌面，简单却扎实，是武汉人快节奏生活里的烟火气。</p><p> <strong style=\"background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);\">江南</strong>：以「精致」为美，苏式汤面、阳春面，讲究汤清面细，是江南人温婉细腻的生活美学。一碗面，就是一方水土的味道。你最爱的是哪一碗？</p>', 15);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (1771957684092, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '3 个秘诀，让你的兰州拉面比店里还好吃', '在家也能做出地道兰州拉面？掌握这 3 个关键技巧，从和面到拉制，让你轻松复刻面馆级口感', 'upload/lanzhoulamian.png', '<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">很多人觉得兰州拉面只有在店里才能吃到正宗味道，其实只要掌握几个核心技巧，在家也能做出筋道十足、汤鲜味美的拉面。</div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">1. 选对面粉是基础</span>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n一定要用高筋面粉，蛋白质含量在 11.5% 以上，这样拉出来的面才够筋道，不容易断。和面时加入少量盐和食用碱水，能让面更有韧性。</div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">2. 醒面时间要足够</span>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n和好的面需要醒面至少 30 分钟，让面筋充分舒展。醒好的面要分成小剂子，刷上油，再醒 20 分钟，这样拉的时候才不会粘在一起。</div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">3. 汤底是灵魂</span>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n正宗的兰州拉面汤底是用牛骨、牛肉和多种香料慢炖 6 小时以上而成。在家可以简化，用牛骨、牛肉、姜片、葱段、八角、桂皮、草果等炖煮，最后撇去浮沫，汤色清澈才是上品。</div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">按照这三个步骤，你也能在家做出一碗让家人赞不绝口的兰州拉面。快去试试</div>', 15);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (1771958409804, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '春季必吃的 5 种时令蔬菜，鲜嫩又营养', '春天是万物生长的季节，也是吃时令蔬菜的最佳时机。这 5 种春季限定蔬菜，错过就要等一年！', 'upload/luntan02.png', '<p>春季的蔬菜带着泥土的清香，口感鲜嫩，营养丰富。以下这 5 种春季时令蔬菜，是餐桌上不可错过的美味：</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>1. 春笋</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>被誉为 “素食第一品”，口感脆嫩，味道清甜。可以用来油焖、清炒或煲汤，是春季餐桌上的常客。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>2. 香椿</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>独特的香气让人欲罢不能，最经典的做法就是香椿炒蛋。香椿富含维生素和矿物质，有清热解毒的功效。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>3. 蚕豆</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>新鲜的蚕豆软糯香甜，无论是清炒、做汤还是做成蚕豆泥，都非常美味。蚕豆富含蛋白质和膳食纤维，是春季的营养佳品。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>4. 马兰头</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>一种常见的野菜，口感清爽，略带苦味。可以凉拌或清炒，有清热解毒、凉血止血的作用。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>5. 荠菜</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>春天的 “报春菜”，味道鲜美，营养丰富。最经典的做法是荠菜饺子或荠菜馄饨，一口下去，满是春天的味道。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>这些春季时令蔬菜，你都吃过吗？赶紧去菜市场找找，把春天的味道搬上餐桌吧！</p>', 14);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (1771959296569, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '从街头到殿堂：火锅的千年演变史', '火锅是中国人最爱的美食之一，它的历史可以追溯到几千年前。从古代的 “温鼎” 到今天的各种火锅，它经历了怎样的演变？', 'upload/luntan03.png', '<p>火锅，这种将食材放入滚汤中涮煮的烹饪方式，已经陪伴中国人走过了数千年的历史。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>起源：商周时期的 “温鼎”</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>最早的火锅雏形可以追溯到商周时期的 “温鼎”，这是一种可以在下面生火加热的鼎，用来保持食物的温度。到了汉代，出现了 “染炉”，可以用来涮煮肉类，这已经和现代火锅非常相似了。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>发展：唐宋时期的 “暖锅”</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>唐宋时期，火锅逐渐普及，出现了 “暖锅”。人们用铜锅或铁锅，将各种食材放入锅中涮煮，边煮边吃。当时的火锅主要以肉类和蔬菜为主，汤底也比较简单。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>兴盛：明清时期的 “火锅宴”</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>明清时期，火锅达到了鼎盛。宫廷中出现了 “火锅宴”，各种珍贵食材如燕窝、鱼翅、鲍鱼等都被用来涮煮。同时，民间也出现了各种特色火锅，如北京的涮羊肉、四川的麻辣火锅等。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>现代：百花齐放的火锅文化</strong>&nbsp;</p><p>如今，火锅已经成为了一种全民美食，各种流派和口味层出不穷。从传统的铜锅涮肉，到现代的九宫格火锅、潮汕牛肉火锅、泰式冬阴功火锅，每一种都有其独特的魅力。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>火锅不仅是一种美食，更是一种社交方式。一家人围坐在火锅旁，边吃边聊，其乐融融。这就是火锅的魅力所在。</p>', 14);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (1771960345147, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '减脂期也能吃的美味：3 款低卡又好吃的三明治', '减脂期不用饿肚子！这 3 款三明治，低卡又饱腹，好吃不胖，让你轻松瘦下来。', 'upload/luntan04.png', '<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">1. 鸡胸肉蔬菜三明治</span></div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<ul style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">食材：全麦面包 2 片、鸡胸肉 100g、生菜、番茄、黄瓜、鸡蛋 1 个</li>\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">做法：鸡胸肉用盐、黑胡椒腌制后煎熟，鸡蛋煮熟切片。将所有食材夹在全麦面包中，即可食用。</li>\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">热量：约 250 大卡</li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">2. 金枪鱼牛油果三明治</span></div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<ul style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">食材：全麦面包 2 片、金枪鱼罐头 50g、牛油果半个、生菜、番茄</li>\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">做法：金枪鱼沥干水分，牛油果压成泥。将金枪鱼和牛油果泥混合，夹在全麦面包中，搭配生菜和番茄。</li>\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">热量：约 300 大卡</li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">3. 鸡蛋火腿三明治</span></div>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<ul style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">食材：全麦面包 2 片、鸡蛋 1 个、低脂火腿 2 片、生菜、黄瓜</li>\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">做法：鸡蛋煎熟，火腿煎至微焦。将所有食材夹在全麦面包中，即可食用。</li>\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">热量：约 220 大卡</li>\n</ul>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">这 3 款三明治，不仅低卡饱腹，而且营养均衡，非常适合减脂期食用。赶紧试试吧！</div>', 14);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (1771960806399, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '又是一年毕业季，我的校园美食记忆', '毕业的脚步越来越近，那些藏在校园角落里的美食，也成了青春里最难忘的味道。今天就来聊聊我的校园美食记忆，也想听听你们学校的故事。\n', 'upload/luntan05.png', '<p>又是一年毕业季，看着校园里穿着学士服拍照的学弟学妹，我也忍不住想起了自己的大学时光。那些年，我们一起在食堂抢过的饭，在宿舍楼下吃过的夜宵，在小吃街逛过的摊位，都成了青春里最温暖的回忆。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>对我来说，校园里最难忘的美食，莫过于三食堂的<strong>番茄鸡蛋面</strong>了。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>每到冬天，下了晚自习，和室友一起冲到食堂，点上一碗热气腾腾的番茄鸡蛋面，酸甜的番茄汤汁裹着劲道的面条，再配上一颗溏心蛋，瞬间就能驱散所有的寒冷和疲惫。还有校门口那家开了十几年的<strong>手抓饼</strong>，阿姨总是会多给我们加一片生菜，刷上满满的甜辣酱，咬下去的每一口都是满足。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>当然，最让人怀念的，还是和同学们一起在宿舍里 “开小灶” 的日子。我们会从超市买来火锅底料和各种食材，在宿舍里用小电锅煮火锅，虽然条件简陋，但大家围坐在一起，边吃边聊，那种热闹和温暖，是任何山珍海味都无法替代的。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>如今，我们已经各奔东西，但那些校园美食的味道，却永远留在了记忆里。它们不仅是填饱肚子的食物，更是我们青春的见证，是我们和同学之间最珍贵的联结。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>那么，<strong>你们学校有哪些让你难忘的美食呢？是食堂的招牌菜，还是校门口的小吃摊？快来评论区和我分享吧！</strong></p>', 14);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (1772046951834, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '隐藏在巷子里的老字号面馆，一碗面吃了 20 年', '在城市的老巷子里，藏着一家开了 20 年的老字号面馆。没有华丽的装修，却靠着一碗地道的牛肉面，俘获了几代人的味蕾。', 'upload/luntan08.png', '<p>在城市的老巷子里，藏着一家开了 20 年的老字号面馆。没有华丽的装修，甚至连招牌都有些褪色，但每天饭点，这里总是座无虚席。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>我第一次来这家店，是朋友带我来的。当时我还在想，不就是一碗面吗，至于这么夸张吗？但当第一口面入口的时候，我就被征服了。面条筋道十足，牛肉炖得软烂入味，汤底清澈鲜美，每一口都是满满的诚意。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>老板是一位年过六旬的老人，从年轻时就开始做面，一做就是一辈子。他说，做面最重要的就是用心，每一根面、每一块肉、每一勺汤，都不能马虎。正是这份坚持，让这家小店在巷子里屹立了 20 年。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>如今，我也成了这家店的常客。每次路过，都会进去点上一碗牛肉面，和老板聊上几句。这里的面，不仅是一种美食，更是一种情怀，一种对传统味道的坚守。</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>如果你也在这座城市，不妨来这家老字号面馆尝尝。相信我，你一定会被这碗面打动的</p><p><br></p>', 14);
INSERT INTO `forum_post` VALUES (1772190652932, '2026-03-24 14:33:38', '挖到宝！这家老城区的糖水铺，是老广的夏日续命神器', '人均 10+，纯手工熬煮，比奶茶还解腻！\n', 'upload/luntan01.png', '<p>逛老城区偶然发现的糖水铺，没有华丽装修，却藏着最地道的广式味道。</p>\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<p><span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">必点清单</span>：</p>\n<ul style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-family: ui-sans-serif, system-ui, sans-serif, \'Apple Color Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Emoji\', \'Segoe UI Symbol\', \'Noto Color Emoji\'; font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">杨枝甘露：芒果 + 西柚 + 椰奶，果肉超足，酸甜清爽，一口入夏！</li>\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">陈皮绿豆沙：熬得沙沙的，陈皮香气浓郁，清热降火，长辈也爱喝。</li>\n<li style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">姜撞奶：现冲现撞，奶香混着姜香，暖乎乎的，适合女生生理期喝。\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-weight: bold; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">小 Tips</span>：糖水都是当天现熬，卖完就关门，建议下午 3 点前到，晚了就没啦！\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n人均：12 元\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n地址：XX 区 XX 路 89 号（靠近老菜市场）\n<div style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-variant-alternates: normal; font-size-adjust: none; font-language-override: normal; font-kerning: auto; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-feature-settings: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; font-variant-position: normal; font-variant-emoji: normal; font-stretch: normal; line-height: 24px; flex: 0 1 auto; flex-direction: row; justify-content: normal; align-items: normal; padding: 0px; margin: 0px; background-image: none; background-position: 0% 0%; background-size: auto; background-repeat: repeat; background-attachment: scroll; background-origin: padding-box; background-clip: border-box;\">&nbsp;</div>\n夏天不想喝奶茶的姐妹，一定要来试试！</li>\n</ul>', 17);
